steps.apply:
Start: {W,X}
Apply WX->Y: {W,X,Y}
Apply WX->Z: {W,X,Y,Z}
Apply WY->X: X already in closure.
Now need V or U: WX->? - no FD gives U or V from W,X,Y,Z alone.
So {W,X}+ = {W,X,Y,Z}.

Check B. WX->V: V not in {W,X,Y,Z}. NOT derivable.
Check A: for A we need VW->YZ. {V,W}+ = {U,V,W} which does NOT contain Y,Z.
